<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>When, i try to convert any unit to or from "micromole per day", i see only the unit "µmol/day" and nothing before this string.</p>

<p>In file Zend/Measure/Flow/Mole.php line 73
we can see "'MICROMOLE_PER_DAY'    =&gt; array(array('' =&gt; 0.000001, '/' =&gt; 86400), 'µmol/day'),"
If i try to convert 1 MICROMOLE_PER_DAY into MICROMOLE_PER_DAY, there should be have the result 1 but i got this string "µmol/day"</p>

<p>For few test, i have change the value 0.000001 into 0.001 and with this value i got a result. For me, there would be a problem with rounded value or something like that.</p>

