            <p>Fixed with SVN-7701.</p>

<p>But you will almost never get the same output because there are always rounding errors and the result depends on the given precision.</p>

<p>Also the internal precision is fixed with 25. So you will never get a result where a precision higher than 25 is recommended.</p>

